        <h2>Content</h2>
        
        <h3>Introduction</h3>
        <p>Welcome to Retro Game Resale, the ultimate platform for buying and selling classic video games and consoles. Whether you're a seasoned collector or someone looking to relive your childhood, we offer a vibrant marketplace, insightful game reviews, and a community for all things retro gaming.</p>
        
        <h3>Buy & Sell Marketplace</h3>
        <p>Our Buy & Sell Marketplace is designed to connect buyers and sellers of classic video games and consoles. This platform provides a user-friendly interface that allows enthusiasts to list their items for sale, browse through listings, and find rare gems to add to their collections. Each listing includes detailed descriptions, images, and pricing information to ensure transparency and trust.</p>
        <img src="https://www.example.com/marketplace-image1.jpg" alt="Marketplace Image 1">
        <img src="https://www.example.com/marketplace-image2.jpg" alt="Marketplace Image 2">
        
        <h3>Game Reviews & Ratings</h3>
        <p>Our Game Reviews & Ratings section provides in-depth analyses of classic games. Our team of experts and community members contribute reviews that cover gameplay, graphics, storyline, and overall experience. This section helps users make informed decisions about which games to add to their collection.</p>
        <img src="https://www.example.com/reviews-image1.jpg" alt="Reviews Image 1">
        <img src="https://www.example.com/reviews-image2.jpg" alt="Reviews Image 2">
        
        <h3>Collector's Corner</h3>
        <p>The Collector's Corner is a special section dedicated to the community of retro gaming collectors. Here, members can share their collections, discuss rare finds, and seek advice on preservation and valuation. This section also features articles on the history of gaming and interviews with prominent collectors.</p>
        <img src="https://www.example.com/collectors-image1.jpg" alt="Collectors Image 1">
        <img src="https://www.example.com/collectors-image2.jpg" alt="Collectors Image 2">
        
